OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry and bright through the
OL,6,Fmorning, then becoming mostly cloudy
OL,7,Fduring the afternoon with a few
OL,8,Fshowers moving across the area. Winds
OL,9,Fgradually ease but remain blustery
OL,10,Falong the coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloudy with showers clearing
OL,13,Feastwards during the evening followed
OL,14,Fby clearing skies. The wind becomes
OL,15,Flight and variable. As temperatures
OL,16,Ffall some ground frost patches could
OL,17,Fform.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
