OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FLargely dry with bright or
OL,6,Fsunny start to Sunday. Turning
OL,7,Fincreasingly cloudy during the
OL,8,Fafternoon with the wind increasing and
OL,9,Fthe chance of some coastal showers
OL,10,Fovernight.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,13,FCloudier on Monday and Tuesday with
OL,14,Fshowers spreading inland from coastal
OL,15,Fareas. Clearing skies with long sunny
OL,16,Fspells on Wednesday. Feeling cooler,
OL,17,Fespecially along windward coastal
OL,18,Fdistricts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
